Detailed Description

Structure to contain information about the structure of the AIPS header file.

Named beginning with a K are offsets with the second character giving the data type:

  • I = integer, offset in type AIPSint,
  • H = Hollerith (character - not null terminated), offset in type gfloat.
  • R = float, offset in type gfloat.
  • D = double, offset in type gdouble.
